# Admin frontend (`frontend/apps/admin`)

## Import aliases

| Alias | Resolves to | Use for |
|-------|-------------|---------|
| `@/` | `src/` | App code (components, features, lib, theme, i18n, app) |
| `@transora/api-client` | workspace package | Generated API client, auth token helpers, `customInstance`, `admin-catalog` |

## Structure

- `src/app/` — router, providers
- `src/features/<domain>/` — pages, drawers, `api/hooks.ts`
- `src/components/ui/FormDrawer.tsx` — **side drawer for all create/edit forms**
- `src/components/map/PointMapPicker.tsx` — Leaflet + OSM geocode
- `src/i18n/locales/{ru,en}/` — `common`, `nav`, `auth`, `dashboard`, `users`, `points`, `nomenclature`, `tariffProfiles`, `refundPolicies`

## Forms & drawers

- **Create/Edit** → `FormDrawer` (slide-in from right), not `Modal`
- **Delete confirm** → `ConfirmDialog` (center)
- **Full editors** (tariff matrix) → dedicated page route
- Use `FormTextField` / `FormSelectField`; layout: `transora-form-stack`, `transora-form-field`
- CSS cascade: `@heroui/styles` → `global.css` → `styles/forms.css` in `index.css`

## API hooks

Wrap `@transora/api-client` functions in `features/*/api/hooks.ts` with React Query. Gate with `enabled: isAuthenticated`.

New catalog endpoints live in `packages/api-client/src/admin-catalog.ts` until Orval regen.

## API client (Orval)

- **Always** use Orval — never edit `packages/api-client/src/generated/**` by hand.
- After backend API changes: `pnpm api:sync` from `frontend/` (backend on `:8080`).
- Domain hooks in `features/*/api/hooks.ts` wrap generated functions (`createFromRoute`, `list1`, …) with React Query; do not reimplement fetch.

## UI & i18n

- HeroUI v3 + Tailwind v4
- All strings via `useTranslation`
- Nav: main items + «Справочники» group (points, nomenclature, refund policies)
